    },
    {
      "start": 713.72,
      "end": 716.2,
      "text": "마치 pelican처럼 사는 법이라든지 말이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 716.38,
      "end": 716.68,
      "text": "Ah."
    },
    {
      "start": 716.78,
      "end": 718.24,
      "text": "We make life too complicated."
    },
    {
      "start": 718.24,
      "end": 721.56,
      "text": "The important things are very simple in my opinion."
    },
    {
      "start": 722.34,
      "end": 725.98,
      "text": "Like food, love, you know, taking care of each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 726.16,
      "end": 726.44,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 726.64,
      "end": 727.12,
      "text": "Pelicans."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.78,
      "end": 731.38,
      "text": "Taking care of each other and pelican도 그랬긴 했네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 731.5,
      "end": 732.24,
      "text": "아버지를 구해줬으니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.24,
      "end": 733.44,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 733.74,
      "end": 737.64,
      "text": "And he rescued, he adopted the baby pelicans."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.84,
      "end": 739.7,
      "text": "But they didn't have a mother or father."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.92,
      "end": 744.06,
      "text": "And he, the pelican, in turn, saved his dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 744.16,
      "end": 745.68,
      "text": "They got each other's backs."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.68,
      "end": 751.4,
      "text": "단순하지만 굉장히 핵심적인 그런 삶의 요소들이 다 있는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 751.52,
      "end": 752.48,
      "text": "펠리컨의 삶에도."
    },
    {
      "start": 753.26,
      "end": 755.24,
      "text": "느껴지는 부분들이 되게 많이 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 755.4,
      "end": 756.1,
      "text": "별게 많아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 756.14,
      "end": 757.04,
      "text": "펠리컨한테."
    },
    {
      "start": 757.16,
      "end": 757.38,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 757.58,
      "end": 758.38,
      "text": "펭귄한테도 그렇고."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.06,
      "end": 759.78,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.86,
      "end": 761.74,
      "text": "갑분 펭귄까지 들어보셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 761.74,
      "end": 763.6,
      "text": "정말 긴장을 늦출 수가 없네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 764.68,
      "end": 765.84,
      "text": "이제 놓아주세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.04,
      "end": 766.2,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.6,
      "end": 767.9,
      "text": "한 번 더 확인해보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 768.66,
      "end": 769.66,
      "text": "I can't believe it."
    },
    {
      "start": 770.14,
      "end": 770.92,
      "text": "It was a miracle."
    },
    {
      "start": 771.52,
      "end": 773.36,
      "text": "My dad was saved by a pelican."
    },
    {
      "start": 773.76,
      "end": 774.66,
      "text": "So it all worked out."
    },
    {
      "start": 775.22,
      "end": 776.42,
      "text": "It's not over yet, Matt."
    },
    {
      "start": 776.98,
      "end": 778.08,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "start": 778.68,
      "end": 779.82,
      "text": "I want to show you something."
    },
    {
      "start": 780.46,
      "end": 781.36,
      "text": "It's a bit of a hike."
    },
    {
      "start": 781.96,
      "end": 782.84,
      "text": "You're going to the board meeting?"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.56,
      "end": 784.48,
      "text": "No, I'm not."
    },
    {
      "start": 784.86,
      "end": 786.28,
      "text": "One thing you'll discover, Matt."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.24,
      "end": 789.5,
      "text": "Sometimes you'll forget the best things you ever learned."
    },
    {
      "start": 789.96,
      "end": 791.4,
      "text": "Like how to live like a pelican."
    },
    {
      "start": 791.4,
      "end": 793.66,
      "text": "네, pelican."
    },
    {
      "start": 793.66,
      "end": 796.34,
      "text": "이렇게 마지막 단어 잘 들어보셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 797.34,
      "end": 802.56,
      "text": "박옥화 님께서 오늘도 편안하게 하루를 굿모닝 팝스와 시작하니 행복해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.96,
      "end": 804.88,
      "text": "크쌤, 로라쌤, 하트 3개."
    },
    {
      "start": 805.18,
      "end": 806.46,
      "text": "오, 하트 4개."
    },
    {
      "start": 806.66,
      "end": 807.52,
      "text": "Back to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 807.78,
      "end": 808.74,
      "text": "하트 3개."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.84,
      "end": 809.82,
      "text": "너무 감사드립니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.1,
      "end": 811.76,
      "text": "4개 잘 받아주시고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 812.44,
      "end": 814.62,
      "text": "오늘은 여기에서 마무리해보도록 할게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 814.94,
      "end": 815.64,
      "text": "See you tomorrow."
    }
  ]
}